access a web site to retrieve or store information.</p>\n<p><strong>For more information</strong></p>\n<p>See [Work with networking in your game](work-with-networking-in-your-directx-game.md).</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","leadings":["","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    ","    "],"nodes":[{"content":"API","pos":[116,119]},{"content":"Description","pos":[142,153]},{"content":"Windows.Networking.Sockets","pos":[216,242]},{"content":"The Windows.Networking.Sockets namespace provides TCP and UDP sockets that allow reliable or unreliable network communication.","pos":[268,394]},{"content":"When to use","pos":[410,421]},{"content":"Use Windows.Networking.Sockets if your game needs to communicate with other computers or devices over the network.","pos":[438,552]},{"content":"For more information","pos":[568,588]},{"content":"See <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Work with networking in your game<ept id=\"p1\">](work-with-networking-in-your-directx-game.md)</ept>.","pos":[605,691],"source":"See [Work with networking in your game](work-with-networking-in-your-directx-game.md)."},{"content":"Windows.Web.HTTP","pos":[742,758]},{"content":"The Windows.Web.HTTP namespace provides a reliable connection to HTTP servers that can be used to access a web site.","pos":[784,900]},{"content":"When to use","pos":[916,927]},{"content":"Use Windows.Web.HTTP when your game needs to access a web site to retrieve or store information.","pos":[944,1040]},{"content":"For more information","pos":[1056,1076]},{"content":"See <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Work with networking in your game<ept id=\"p1\">](work-with-networking-in-your-directx-game.md)</ept>.","pos":[1093,1179],"source":"See [Work with networking in your game](work-with-networking-in-your-directx-game.md)."}]},{"content":"Support Utilities - Libraries that build on the Windows 10 APIs.","